ow the\ndynamics of the collapse with a non-convex EoS departs from the convex case,\nleaving distinctive imprints on the gravitational waveforms. The astrophysical\nsignificance of these results for microphysical EoSs is discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Jun 2018 18:21:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 24 Jan 2019 09:55:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-28"}
