/4-BPS black holes are precisely weighted\nby the BPS index predicted from the DVV formula, including the detailed moduli\ndependence. We also extract two-instanton corrections from pairs of 1/2-BPS\nblack holes, demonstrating consistency with supersymmetry and wall-crossing,\nand estimate the size of instanton-anti-instanton contributions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Jun 2018 19:29:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 6 Jun 2019 21:08:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-11"}
